Streets of Brooklyn Heights & DUMBO

The Streets of Brooklyn Heights & DUMBO is the second photography documentary project in our new series, “Life After The Pandemic.” Our goal is to explore various areas of New York: capturing the culture around it, as well as examine the effects of the pandemic.

What's Your Story 

Here is the photoshoot that was taken alongside the commercial "What's your Story"

Actors: Fulvio Della Volta, Jake Goldberg, Mackenzie Mercer

@elonproductions

History's Most Memorable Speeches

This is an NFT collection of some of the most memorable speeches made by historical American figures. No matter the political party, it's important to preserve these speeches, as each of them tells an important story about the landscape of American culture at that time. 

As YouTube and other social media companies continue to censor and take down content, the potential to lose some of America's history is also at risk. This NFT collection revolves around the theme of voice and freedom of speech.

America was founded on the principle of freedom of speech and we must find ways to preserve this principle.Own a piece of American History before it's too late
